{"tid":557972,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"呢兩張相其實係一模一樣?","createTime":"2018-02-12T00:11:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-12T03:50:32.000Z","uid":72478,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c10cfc721cd946f50bcfcb58a19caf51fca34214","tid":557972,"uid":72478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T00:11:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/L8swkHh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FL8swkHh.jpg&h=67bf46f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日，國外論壇Reddit上的兩張照片發佈僅2天時間就吸引了200萬人圍觀，不少網友都認為這是兩張不同拍攝角度的照片，但其實它們一模一樣！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/e2d8ab71ly1foctx9qpstg20ck08whdx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwx2.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2Fe2d8ab71ly1foctx9qpstg20ck08whdx.gif&h=23f9d08e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有網友利用Photoshop將右邊的圖挪到左邊，發現兩張照片完全重疊，也就證明了這兩張照片其實就是同一張照片。<br />\n<br />\n有網友留言稱，未來有一天如果人工智慧真的統治地球時，我們或許能夠用這兩張照片來區分人類和機器人，機器人可以一眼看出兩張照片是同一張，而人類則會認為是不同的照片。<br />\n<br />\n類似的錯覺照片還有2007 Best Illusion of the Year比賽的獲獎作品The Leaning Tower Illusion，同樣是將同一張照片複製粘貼，但右邊的看起來卻傾斜的更多。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/02/20180211_gtz_412_7/gamersky_02origin_03_20182112128E55.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F02%2F20180211_gtz_412_7%2Fgamersky_02origin_03_20182112128E55.jpg&h=65d0a7b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實，我們之所以出現這種錯覺，是因為視覺系統將兩張照片當作一個整體場景來看。平時我們看街景的時候，每條向遠方延伸的直線都會聚集在消失點，但是圖中的直線卻是平行的，我們的大腦假設了這倆張照片會有相同的消失點，所以右邊看上去會更加傾斜。<br />\n<br />\n　類似的例子還有很多，比如將兩邊排列整齊的樹木，或者平行的鐵軌照片複製粘貼放在一起看，也有出現這種錯覺的情況。"},{"pid":"baf09e2d442616fa8e4d6ef9da5145fb42bdb722","tid":557972,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T00:13:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9519d1f23afddae3449d5e30e36c875e9d7e95ad","tid":557972,"uid":32577,"like":4,"dislike":31,"score":-27,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T00:16:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁我應該係AI 一望就知一樣"},{"pid":"756b4817c7c415560fd1b20159ac08a90cef4750","tid":557972,"uid":4346,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"quote":{"pid":"9519d1f23afddae3449d5e30e36c875e9d7e95ad","tid":557972,"uid":32577,"like":4,"dislike":31,"score":-27,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T00:16:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁我應該係AI 一望就知一樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T00:17:06.000Z","msg":"又係你條撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d4045c986cdb29db7e858abfcee7c713b83a303","tid":557972,"uid":15358,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"756b4817c7c415560fd1b20159ac08a90cef4750","tid":557972,"uid":4346,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"quote":{"pid":"9519d1f23afddae3449d5e30e36c875e9d7e95ad","tid":557972,"uid":32577,"like":4,"dislike":31,"score":-27,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T00:16:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁我應該係AI 一望就知一樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T00:17:06.000Z","msg":"又係你條撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T00:22:34.000Z","msg":"又係你條撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11ba16a05ff14fccbfe33b7ea81864dc16567293","tid":557972,"uid":16046,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T01:08:58.000Z","msg":"完全唔覺得有分別"},{"pid":"73c34ab862a8c8d2fedd52dafa4417843abb3fec","tid":557972,"uid":101968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9519d1f23afddae3449d5e30e36c875e9d7e95ad","tid":557972,"uid":32577,"like":4,"dislike":31,"score":-27,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T00:16:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁我應該係AI 一望就知一樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T01:12:51.000Z","msg":"AI死全家"},{"pid":"af607c423f8ee408ae635941bbbf47d3f4