tz_412_7/gamersky_02origin_03_20182112128E55.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F02%2F20180211_gtz_412_7%2Fgamersky_02origin_03_20182112128E55.jpg&h=65d0a7b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實，我們之所以出現這種錯覺，是因為視覺系統將兩張照片當作一個整體場景來看。平時我們看街景的時候，每條向遠方延伸的直線都會聚集在消失點，但是圖中的直線卻是平行的，我們的大腦假設了這倆張照片會有相同的消失點，所以右邊看上去會更加傾斜。<br />\n<br />\n　類似的例子還有很多，比如將兩邊排列整齊的樹木，或者平行的鐵軌照片複製粘貼放在一起看，也有出現這種錯覺的情況。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T02:05:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb108a6e7b27b49116eff8e825eeec6f61c17b1e","tid":557972,"uid":92871,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T03:40:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/113916_822d2c306353a781a069e9c7b966f464.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F113916_822d2c306353a781a069e9c7b966f464.gif&h=9e1ecc6b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/113935_eb940802de17e4315084b3719969c50d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F113935_eb940802de17e4315084b3719969c50d.gif&h=fc314dcc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f4f40626f8673d80e4b6cc80c6eda98078a208a","tid":557972,"uid":65774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58aa738a301341949cbdbacfafa3b4d54e262b64","tid":557972,"uid":42469,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b11e5f023b949f20f1e58314bb3d118bd148d3a0","tid":557972,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T01:44:33.000Z","msg":"睇個底都要一樣啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n眼盲就驗眼啦傻鳩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T01:56:58.000Z","msg":"其實你咁唔叫叻，只係公佈比大家知你係三維處理上有先天缺憾<br />\n即係腦殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T03:50:32.000Z